Come aboard this palatial cruise for the experience of a lifetime. Lace up your skates for a spin around the rink, or kick back and catch dazzling ice skating spectaculars and 3D movies. Taste your way from Italy to Japan at restaurants like Giovanni’\s Table and Izumi. And much more.

Welcome aboard Voyager of the Seas.\nFilled with glittering skyscrapers, Singapore practically hums with business and trade. You\'ll also find multi-ethnic culture, great cuisine and attractions that include modern malls, traditional shops, colonial buildings and historic temples.
Day 2 \nARRIVES 8:00 AM DEPARTS 7:00 PM (DOCKED)\nPort of Call: Kuala Lumpur (Port Klang), Malaysia

Kuala Lumpur is a bustling hub for business, media and the arts. There are luxury hotels, mega-malls and skyscrapers as well as heritage architecture and multicultural ambiance in districts like Merdeka Square, Chinatown and Little India.

Whether you seek an adrenaline rush or total tranquility, our ships have it all. Try rock climbing, ice skating and mini golf on green that overlooks a sea of blue. Melt away land-based stress with a spa massage, build a scrapbook of memories or simply relax poolside.
Day 4 \nARRIVES 8:00 AM\nPort of Call: Singapore, Singapore

On behalf of the India Leadership Team, we would like to officially welcome you to our national offsite in Hyderabad. In the next two days, collectively we will join forces and wake up to a new Sunrise!


Be prepared to learn more about our 2030 vision, discover how we are embracing agility with a spirit of Yatte Minahare and learn about our powerhouse portfolio. Importantly, let’s celebrate our 2018 team effort responsibly and understand our 2019 objectives.


The successful growth of our company is the direct result of you, our valued employees, our #1 priority, so we hope that you walk away with a better understanding of the important role you will play in helping us deliver our business the right way-the ApekSHAH Way!


We have a full agenda ahead of us, however, we are looking forward to spending time with all of you as we actively embrace the Sunrise and Unleash our Spirit!
